title: Johan van der Keuken - Lucebert, time & farewell (1994)
description:
DVDrip - Srt subtitles included: english, french and spanish

A tryptich about his friend, poet & painter Lucebert. First part was a Tv command, second part is more like a free association game, and the last posthumous part is a visit @ Lucebert's home, somewhat trying to find his ghost between all his paintings.
